<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main class="overview-page" style="max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 104px 24px 64px;">
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="hero-container">
    <div class="hero-text-block">
      <span class="legal-eyebrow" style="color: var(--google-blue);">SYSTEMS ARCHITECT & CYBERSECURITY ENGINEER</span>
      <h1 class="hero-headline">
        I build secure, scale-proof foundations for digital systems.
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        A systems engineer with a high-conviction mindset. I design and build robust multi-tenant backend engines, configure hardware-isolated mobile secure vaults, and establish secure telemetry grids. No generic templates, no technical compromises.
      </p>
      
      <div class="btn-group" style="display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-top: 24px;">
        <a href="/verification" class="btn-g primary" style="text-decoration: none;">Verify Code Ledgers &rarr;</a>
        <a href="/console" class="btn-g secondary" style="text-decoration: none;">Launch Systems Console</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="hero-image-block">
      <div class="profile-image-frame">
        <img src="/images/New background image  Of mutasim billah (1).png" alt="Mutasim Billah" class="profile-photo" />
        <div class="image-coordinate-tag">MUTASIM_NODE_01</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Engineering Mindset & Principles -->
  <div style="margin-top: 64px;">
    <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light); padding-bottom: 12px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-dark); margin-bottom: 4px;">Engineering Principles & Mindset</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0;">The core execution guardrails that dictate my systems architecture design.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="principles-grid">
      <!-- Principle 1 -->
      <div class="principle-card">
        <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved" style="color: var(--google-red);"></i> Zero-Trust by Default</h3>
        <p>Security is never an afterthought. From hardware Keystore key isolation in mobile apps and double-submit CSRF buffer matching to file-threat ClamAV scans, I build layers designed to withstand analysis.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Principle 2 -->
      <div class="principle-card">
        <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-network-wired" style="color: var(--google-blue);"></i> Scale-Proof Architecture</h3>
        <p>Architecting multi-process monoliths designed for vertical stability. Utilizing Redis Pub/Sub core clustering and stateless session storage mappings to ensure expansion doesn't introduce code fragility.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Principle 3 -->
      <div class="principle-card">
        <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt" style="color: var(--google-yellow);"></i> AI-Accelerated Velocity</h3>
        <p>Leveraging specialized AI development models to scaffold, audit, and patch systems code. Bypassing traditional cycle bottlenecks to deliver validated features at 4x normal velocity.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Principle 4 -->
      <div class="principle-card">
        <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-code" style="color: var(--google-green);"></i> Zero Compromises</h3>
        <p>Obsessive focus on clean, high-performance execution. No unnecessary bloat, no placeholders, and fully optimized memory and security boundaries across all platforms.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
